{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      The \"See It Working\" Page\n      Inspiration: Housecall Pro, HoneyBook\n      Hero: Your 3-phone mockup showing Boss OS for 3 industries — but INTERACTIVE. The Towkay taps between industries and sees the dashboard change. Sales numbers, staff on duty, cash flow — all moving, all real-looking.\n      Below: ROI calculator (\"You're losing RM X,XXX/month to manual work\") → 5 core features with animated UI previews → Industry cards (click to see your vertical) → Pricing with savings math → WhatsApp CTA\n      Why it works: Interactive demos boost conversion 86%. The Towkay's #1 fear is \"can I actually use this?\" — showing the UI kills that fear instantly. No \"book a demo\" gate.\n      Completeness: 9/10 — Full funnel, interactive, industry-specific. Most work to build but highest conversion potential.","choice":"approach-a","id":null,"timestamp":1775339162457}
